<div id="about_popup" class="simple_popup mfp-hide">
  <h3>About</h3>
  <p>PIONEERS is an interactive study of the impact of pioneers in the field of computer science. With PIONEERS you can visualize the "who", "what" and "where" of contributions to any set of topics in our varied field.</p>
  <div>
    <p>The <strong>who</strong> page will present each pioneer and their relative importance, via radius, for the chosen tag(s).</p>
    <ul>
      <li>More impactful people will appear larger</li>
      <li>"Importance" is calculated relatively based on the amount and overall impact of each matching achievement</li>
      <li>When hovered, headshots will zoom in</li>
      <li>When clicked, zoomed in headshots will present the matching achievements in an overlay</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div>
    <p>The <strong>when</strong> page presents a timeline of achievements for the chosen tag(s).</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Radii of the halo around each point will indicate impact</li>
      <li>When hovered, achievement details will be revealed</li>
      <li>When clicked, zoomed in achievements will present the matching achievements in an overlay</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
